On Friday 15 November 2024, I had prawn scrambled egg rice and spicy popcorn chicken for my lunch at Keat Hong Food Centre & Market outlet within Keat Hong Shopping Centre at Choa Chu Kang, and the prawn scrambled egg rice and spicy popcorn chicken tasted very delicious as I liked this meal. Overall, the service provided to me was very good and I would love to try these other delightful scrambled egg rice dishes (except Beef and Pork) from other Egg Talk outlets in the future.

At first I was wary because there were other similar concept stalls in Sunshine Place that the food tasted bad.
However, it turn out to be Delicious! The rice is the best! $4.50 for beancurd roll and $$7.50 for prawn paste chicken egg rice. 10% discount with fairprice app

Awesome food, friendly staff.

Been there multiple times, no regrets to give this place the credit it deserve.
